n weekends we played so late that we forgot about this and would get booted to desktop while the virus program was starting to scan the hard drive. Especially annoying if we were in the middle of soloing something ... <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :| --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/indifferent.gif ALT=":|"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  (Yes, we either disabled this or changed the scheduled time later on.)<br>
